Responsibilities

  Design, develop, test, and launch web applications and microservices
  Participate in full software development life cycle
  Work in teams or individually to develop new web applications / microservices
  Review and resolve reported bugs
  Gather requirements from users (internal and external)
  Ensure good code quality and documentation

Requirements

  Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma, Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate Diploma/Professional Degree in Engineering (Computer/Telecommunication), Computer Science/Information Technology or equivalent.
  At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.
  Required Skill(s): PHP, Laravel, JavaScript, VueJS, MySQL, HTML, CSS, jQuery
  Preferably Junior Executive specialized in IT/Computer - Software or equivalent.

Bonus!

  Passionate, like very passionate about coding (show us what you have!)
  Have done side programming projects
  Has experience building / consuming APIs
  Never give up attitude!

